This repository contains all the basic programs written in python3
This will help in revising basic logic
List of completed programs:
1) Palindrome (palindrome.py)
2) Reverse Pyramid (rev_pyramid.py)
3) String Reversal (str_reverse.py)
4) Reverse of right angle triangle (rev_right_triangle.py)
5) Printing a pyramid (pyramid.py)
6) Printing a mirror of pyramid (helix_pyramid.py)
7) Printing a right angle triangle (right_angle_pattern.py)
8) Reversal of an integer (interger_reversal.py)
9) FizzBuzz (fizz_buzz.py)
10) Printing most frequent character in a string (max_char.py)
11) Checking if two words are anagrams (anagram.py)
12) Dividing a given array into the given length of chunks (array_chunking.py)
13) Capitalizing each word of a given sentence (sentence_capitalization.py)
